query:
UPDATE auditInstances ai
JOIN auditTypes at ON ai.auditTypeId = at.id
JOIN auditTemplates atem ON at.id = atem.auditTypeId AND atem.isActive = 1
SET ai.auditTemplateId = atem.id
WHERE ai.auditTemplateId IS NULL;
